Assignment Title: Task Management Dashboard
Objective: Build a simple Task Management Dashboard using multiple components and
modules where users can view, add (without forms), and update tasks dynamically.
Requirements
1. 2. 3. 4. 5. 6. 7. Use Angular Modules to organize the app (e.g., TaskModule, SharedModule).
Use multiple components (e.g., TaskListComponent, TaskItemComponent,
TaskActionsComponent).
Tasks should have a name, status (Pending/In Progress/Completed), and priority.
Tasks should be displayed in a list with an option to update status & delete.
NO FORMS & NO ROUTING should be used.
Use Angular Services to manage tasks.
Use parent-child communication between components